 Justification:
 Funding decrease of $394K from FY 2025 to FY 2026 applied to EMI Hardware (MA004), Software Fixes (MA104) procurements and EMI Control Instrumentation.

 MA004 (EMI HDW Fixes) OPN Funds are used to procure and install (P/I) EMI Fixes on deploying ships and submarines. The number of EMI Fixes procured (MA004 Hardware Fixes) are dependent on the
 number of ships/submarines in the Fleet and when they deploy.

 MA104 (EMI SFW Fixes) procures and installs SFW Fixes to mitigate electromagnetic interference (EMI). This effort retains responsibility for the procurement of models and frequency management techniques
 that are encompassed by other Navy tools (e.g., Real-Time Spectrum Operations).

 MA204 (EMI Control Instrumentation) procures and installs specialized test equipment for HW and SW products in collecting data to provide corrective measures.




