 Justification:
 FY 2027 funding provides for:
 - Procurement of four (4) SMRC Multiband Radios with twenty (20) pieces of ancillary equipment, for installation in FY 2029.
 - Installation of six (6) SMRC Multiband Radios. These units were procured in FY 2025 for installation in FY 2027.

 - Procurement of four (4) SMRC Multiband Upgrade Kits with thirty-two (32) pieces of ancillary equipment, for installation in FY 2029.
 - Installation of three (3) SMRC Multiband Upgrade Kits. These units were procured in FY 2025 for installation in FY 2027.
 - Procurement of seven (7) enhancements for Dynamic Local Scanning (DLS) and Single Channel Ground and Airborne Radio System (SINCGARS) upgrade (eDSu), for installation in FY 2028.

 - Procurement of ten (10) SMRC Sub with ten (10) pieces of SMRC Sub ancillary equipment, for installation in FY 2028.
 - Procurement of thirty-nine (39) SMRC HF with thirty-nine (39) pieces of SMRC HF ancillary equipment, for installation in FY 2028.




